{
  "text": "Factors that should be considered in the optimization of the membrane module are the shape of the membrane module, the placement of the module, hydraulic conditions, the diameter and the length as well as the tightness of the hollow fiber filaments [CITATION_1] . As can be seen from Figure 8 , the wall shear stress inside the membrane component decreased with the increase in the length of the filament.",
